   Bulrush Restaurant

    Bulrush is a Michelin Star restaurant in Cotham owned by Chef George
                                  Livesey.

                               Opening times:

                                   Lunch:

                    Thursday - Saturday 12.30pm - 2.30pm
                                   Dinner:
                     Tuesday - Saturday 6.30pm - 8.30pm
                  Bulrush is closed on Sundays and Mondays.

